  "texts": [
    "The selected databases included DOAJ, Science Direct, PubMed, and IEEE Xplore, all known for housing an extensive collection of pertinent articles.",
    "Additionally, we included other papers through manual searches on Google Scholar to encompass a broader range of literature.",
    "The eligibility criteria protocol for the selection of papers in this review is shown in Table 4.",
    "Data SelectionThe search across three distinct databases yielded a cumulative total of 841 papers, as depicted in the PRISMA [25] flowchart (Fig. 2).",
    "This chart delineates the process through stages of identification, screening, and inclusion."
  ]
}